According to Moeti Mmusi, Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison spokesperson, the accident happened on Samora Machel Drive close to Nelsville. The three that were killed included the driver and a passenger in the minibus, and the driver of the sedan. Photo credit: Mbombela Fire & Rescue They were all declared dead at the scene. “The cause of the crash remains unclear at this stage and an investigation is underway. No further injuries were recorded,” Mmusi concluded. Photo credit: Mbombela Fire & Rescue ALSO READ: A tale of Kruger’s beloved K9 hero, Killer